      "message": "You should be aware that serializing an int64 with \u003e 52 bits to JSON will round to the nearest float64.\nhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\n\nWe have jsonutils.Number to (semi-)transparently encode to string.\nhttps://skia.googlesource.com/buildbot/+/master/go/jsonutils/jsonutils.go#12",
